  "texts": [
    "To evaluate whether the models' responses are of high quality and meet the desired criteria (e.g., answering outof-context questions when appropriately triggered), we use GPT-3.5-turbo-0125 along with a predefined template to compare generated responses to ground-truth answers.",
    "The template states: \"You are a model response quality investigator.",
    "Check whether the two responses express similar meanings.\"",
    "The ground-truth responses, also generated by GPT-3.5-turbo-0125, are detailed in Section 5.2 and 5.3.",
    "We run each experiment three times and report the average results."
  ],
